{"tid":1665593,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"To all the Muslims across the word","createTime":"2019-10-20T15:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T17:15:40.000Z","uid":85745,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"874f6ff7d111ca2d8a3cafc257feec38dcb5e27a","tid":1665593,"uid":85745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:29:21.000Z","msg":"One of the reasons for Hong Kong being an international city is we respect any race and religion. That's why Hong Kong is an multicultural city which suits everyone.<br />\n<br />\nWith our greatest respect, we would like to apologize on behalf of all the HongKongers to all the Muslims regarding the misconduct of the police early in this afternoon. We all feel ashamed on our regimes. We live in a police state that our leaders don't care about the freedom. <br />\n<br />\nAs regards the censorship on NBA and Movie industry, the evilness of CCP has already spread across the world.We hope everyone can stand with Hong Kong, fight against the China's dictatorship."},{"pid":"4b1671f4204e302d48dabd9db10bf3b5c77a4eb0","tid":1665593,"uid":48948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:29:38.000Z","msg":"而家popo喺清真寺洗緊地，咁幾時洗埋條彌敦道？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665397\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665397</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"418f76726f3c0ebded2f7b9e81393cbfa1713283","tid":1665593,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uAe0u7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuAe0u7e.jpg&h=01c93cc2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1268b638246f0c68ddae0ccd13e8afa624b2f7c2","tid":1665593,"uid":95761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"418f76726f3c0ebded2f7b9e81393cbfa1713283","tid":1665593,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.c